WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:25.495
Dear viewers, dear readers of Večernji
list and viewers of this form of ours, we

00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:29.655
have an extraordinary show, namely the
first time that politics is

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:31.680
being filmed outside the studio.

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:36.895
This is because we are in Medjugorje and
not with just anyone, but with one of the

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:39.640
six Medjugorje visionaries,
Ivan Dragičević.

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:42.400
Ivana, Jesus and Mary are praised.
Welcome.

00:00:42.440 --> 00:00:43.960
Thank you for your time.

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:50.040
Thank you too, for allowing me to
be your guest and God's blessing.

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:55.495
Let's go, we are actually in the novena,
or rather on the eve of the 45th

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:57.960
anniversary of the Medjugorje phenomenon.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.040
That's why we met.

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:02.000
Here's what's happening
in Medjugorje these days.

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:06.720
Come on, tell me a little bit about it
for people who can't come to Medjugorje.

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:09.800
What's the atmosphere like
in Medjugorje these days?

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:11.160
Let's start with that.

00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:14.960
So you, as you can see for yourself?

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:20.335
You are present here, there is an
intensive program, there

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:22.680
is a lot of prayer.
A lot.

00:01:22.760 --> 00:01:28.720
The trip to the apparition hill
where as a parish at four o'clock.

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:34.175
Here are the prayers in my chapel Mary
goes from the called

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:36.160
Lady to the hill Mary.

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:40.480
That's how she goes to
the hill and 11 o'clock.

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:44.160
So people are really us wherever you go.

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:47.760
People are in prayer, walking, praying.

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:54.015
I would say, it is a special moment for
all of us and for people who

00:01:54.040 --> 00:01:56.280
come to Medjugorje often.

00:01:56.400 --> 00:02:04.015
This is for N1 a moment where we, where we
all go back to the beginning and to renew

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:10.480
what Our Lady calls us to and where
she leads us, and leads us to Jesus.

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:15.240
Yes, it really is, you can
feel a spiritual charge.

00:02:15.320 --> 00:02:20.775
Especially hot, very hot and I would like
to go back 45 years in

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.960
these warm, hot June days.

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:25.320
It was also hot, wasn't it?

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:30.375
When Our Lady appeared, how was it and
here is what you can

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:32.760
remember from June 24, 1981.

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:37.360
We will never be able to
get out of my memories.

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:40.720
And now as I stand, I sit with you.

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:43.360
Emotions are present there.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:47.120
Every day that approaches that day.
24.

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:53.535
And I personally, reviewing my archives,
records through these days

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:56.200
that I wrote down carefully?

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:57.960
Simply, that's me.

00:02:58.040 --> 00:02:59.840
That's so much joy.

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:02.160
That comes to the heart.

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:08.160
It's a grace that is indescribably
difficult to put into words.

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:14.080
That gift that God gave me, how
can I thank you for all of it.

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:22.095
I was a child at the time, 81 years old, I
was 16 years old, I was the oldest of the

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:29.600
children in the family, I have two even
younger brothers, a mother and a father.

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:30.920
At that time.

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:38.295
We worked hard as during communism,
helping our parents to complete school so

00:03:38.320 --> 00:03:44.575
that they could have some means of living,
we herded sheep, herded

00:03:44.600 --> 00:03:46.480
cattle, picked sage.

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:49.360
And most of all about tobacco.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:56.535
Even though I was the oldest in the
family, I always had to be the first to

00:03:56.560 --> 00:04:00.600
show the younger ones
that they had to sit.

00:04:00.680 --> 00:04:06.960
And every day in that hard work,
getting up at five in the morning.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:11.920
Mother calls, and we have
to finish with the spirit.

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:18.000
Before the sun came up, the tobacco
was harvested in the summer.

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:26.280
And so every day you go to pick tobacco
and you come home seemingly lower.

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:30.120
That tobacco raises it
on the pile, dries it.

00:04:30.200 --> 00:04:36.135
And every day in that hard work as a child
I always asked my mother if

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:39.440
it was some feast day of St.
Anastasia.

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:45.200
And I knew when the saint comes or
I couldn't sleep a little longer.

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:48.960
Well, that day came Wednesday, 2.
4.6. 1981.

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:50.720
The feast day of St.

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:52.240
John the Baptist.

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:56.080
That morning I slept on
my mother's neck too.

00:04:56.160 --> 00:05:02.815
Does my mother come to my room in Buda
five or six times and that I have to get

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:08.120
up as soon as possible to get
ready because we're already late?

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:13.535
And you know how children are at that
time, when you don't have

00:05:13.560 --> 00:05:15.480
to go to the field yet.

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:18.320
I liked to sleep a little longer.

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:24.415
And there wasn't much thinking, I come two
or three times, at that time

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:26.720
there weren't many changes.

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:28.480
To have a nice mass.

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:32.800
What are you going to do
at mass, another work day?

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:38.680
Soon you go to your room as if you
woke up your two younger brothers.

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:44.520
And your mother is waiting on the
macadam road in front of the house.

00:05:44.600 --> 00:05:47.640
And we quickly go to mass at 11 a.
m.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:51.480
I remember it as clearly
as if it were today.

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:56.855
I was at mass, I'm not sure about the
body, but I was there

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.600
with my heart and soul.

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:02.520
When the children wake up,
they're sleepy, nothing.

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:04.760
Some pushing doesn't work.

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:08.800
I was at mass.

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:13.000
I was just waiting for it
to end as soon as possible.

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:16.720
And when I thought it
would end, we came home.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:22.120
My mother's custom was for her
father to ask us something like this.

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:26.360
How many people were present
at the mass we attended?

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:31.655
How many of us listened to the Gospel and
my mother asked me Ivane

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:33.720
in which Gospel today was.

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:34.880
I didn't know.

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:41.080
But my mother, like every mother, knows
how to draw attention to what is said.

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:46.400
You have to listen to the priest,
you have to listen to the sermon.

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:52.000
Mass and you always go to mass to
listen to the priest and after that.

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:58.040
It was always a tradition for us to
stay together for lunch, a family lunch.

00:06:58.120 --> 00:06:59.360
Sarma.
That day.

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:04.575
We ate meat baked under the peka when it
was yesterday and before

00:07:04.600 --> 00:07:06.320
the end of that lunch.

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:11.360
Three friends from the village
with whom I went to school come.

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:16.520
They come in front of my parents'
house and call, they say to me.

00:07:16.600 --> 00:07:22.000
They call me by name Ivane, come
with us, There are not enough of us.

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:25.840
Let's go play football,
and it's not our custom.

00:07:25.920 --> 00:07:32.015
It's always a holiday somewhere in the
meadow, and right across the road, the

00:07:32.040 --> 00:07:36.440
buses stop here under the
apparition hill in the meadow.

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:42.055
There was a time when Jakov was my mother
and we always gathered there

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:43.960
on Sundays and holidays.

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:46.120
We were playing soccer.

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:49.880
I didn't need to be told twice.
I got up.

00:07:49.960 --> 00:07:56.040
I immediately went with him and the
dirt road that was there before.

00:07:56.120 --> 00:08:02.240
And we came to that meadow around
three and a half in the afternoon.

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:05.800
We played soccer until about 5 o'clock.

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:08.960
Maybe a little before we finished.

00:08:09.040 --> 00:08:15.655
And when we finished soccer, we left that
meadow and went up to this road

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:18.360
that goes up towards Cenacolo.

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:20.760
That road was a dirt road.

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:24.495
An asphalt road that essentially goes
through Bijakovići and

00:08:24.520 --> 00:08:25.960
where you go up the hill.

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:33.440
All of that used to be macadam field
roads where cows, sheep, goats used to go.

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:39.615
And people used to use them where they
bought hay where they cut

00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:42.640
bushes and so on for everything.

00:08:42.760 --> 00:08:49.335
People more or less all had sheep, horses,
cows and used the roads so

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:52.040
they could feed that one too.

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:54.600
When we finished that one.

00:08:54.680 --> 00:09:02.095
When we were already tired, we slowly
walked out of that meadow onto that road

00:09:02.120 --> 00:09:05.520
and on that road we met three girls.

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:09.640
They were Ivanka, Mirjana and Vicka.
Vicka.

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:17.280
I knew her well because he went to the
same school who is a year older than her.

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:20.920
And I knew the other two girls myself.

00:09:21.040 --> 00:09:25.840
Not so well because they
didn't live in Medjugorje.

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:28.080
Ivanka lived in Mostar.

00:09:28.160 --> 00:09:35.655
Mirjana lived in Sarajevo, they only came
to their grandparents over the summer

00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:43.015
because everyone was here on summer
vacation to spend time here with them and

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:49.400
not a single friend who was with
me, and ask those two what they do.

00:09:49.520 --> 00:09:56.120
They said they were going for a walk,
to look for the sheep's parents.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.760
I didn't ask anything.

00:09:58.840 --> 00:10:04.520
I was very, very withdrawn then,
shy now and didn't communicate much.

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:10.015
At that time I just waited on the
sidelines for them to finish my

00:10:10.040 --> 00:10:13.760
conversation with them
and for us to move on.

00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:17.000
They moved on, up to now 200 Cenacolo.

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:21.040
There were two fences
where the sheep were kept.

00:10:21.160 --> 00:10:22.480
That one didn't.

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:25.120
These go where I always say up.

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:32.135
Most of my family goes to the village, and
since my house is from my parents', it's

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:35.280
only a village away towards the field.

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:37.600
One friend, Ivan Ivanković.

00:10:37.680 --> 00:10:39.640
And that I was with him.

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:45.615
Come on, come with me so he can get
something to eat and change and we

00:10:45.640 --> 00:10:48.440
can come back to your place later.

00:10:48.520 --> 00:10:54.480
We watched Cibona and Bosna play that
day and watch basketball together.

00:10:54.520 --> 00:11:00.735
The television has one small television,
black and white, and this used to

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:03.480
be the television in the village.

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:08.655
The first one in the village had those
families whose parents

00:11:08.680 --> 00:11:10.360
had been in Germany.

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:15.640
They live in Germany, so he could
have brought it from Germany.

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:21.895
I always gathered in one of those five or
six families when there was football or

00:11:21.920 --> 00:11:25.720
basketball and we watched
football and basketball.

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:28.480
And that's how it was that evening.

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:30.080
And we went to them.

00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:34.120
We watched the first half
of that game at his place.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:40.015
And I tell you, my friend, come to my
house to grab something to eat quickly

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:43.080
and come back later for the second half.

00:11:43.160 --> 00:11:47.800
We quickly crossed the field
and came to the end of the cafe.

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:49.640
And where is Ivano now?

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:54.695
You know, it's practically impossible not
to come home across the

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:56.760
field and come to my house.

00:11:56.840 --> 00:12:02.120
I grabbed something to eat quickly
and we're slowly walking this way.

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:07.960
Now we went from my mother's house to my
mother's house for the second half,

00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:10.760
but we didn't get there until today.

00:12:10.840 --> 00:12:14.280
But this second half
something else happened.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:18.160
That road we walked was a
very narrow goat's path.

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:23.640
Walking along that road, we don't go back
to the garden under my house,

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:25.520
where I've already been.

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:31.000
And then there were five or six trees
of those green apples and people.

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:36.640
And me and my friends said let's grab
a game and we'll have a little bit.

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:40.440
The T-shirts were white
and they had an entrance.

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:46.480
We took a few apples and went out
on the road again and kept going.

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:47.360
Going on.

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:51.920
We heard a voice from afar,
no one was calling us.

00:12:52.040 --> 00:12:57.160
We didn't see anyone on the
road we were on at that time.

00:12:57.240 --> 00:13:03.135
Everything was overgrown with bushes and
there was nothing in the

00:13:03.160 --> 00:13:05.120
greenery of one house.

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:07.120
Just a fence, a path.

00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:10.600
What cows and sheep could have walked.

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:15.160
We heard a voice saying
that we didn't see anyone.

00:13:15.280 --> 00:13:17.880
We didn't pay much attention.

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:23.680
And the next day, we heard that
voice getting closer and louder.

00:13:23.800 --> 00:13:27.720
At one point we turned
around and saw Vicka.

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:34.000
A girl we had met before after
football was standing in one position.

00:13:34.120 --> 00:13:41.200
Now, if the wind blows, the secretary
leaves when you get out on the main road.

00:13:41.280 --> 00:13:46.815
She was standing in that very place and
calling the two of us

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:49.080
with her trembling voice.

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:51.160
We turned towards her.

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:57.135
We were quite far from them because we
were at that house of that

00:13:57.160 --> 00:14:00.400
monastery here under the Blue Cross.

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:02.640
There was a fence there.

00:14:02.720 --> 00:14:08.560
And that's where we stopped because
we heard that voice so close.

00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:10.440
And she was running.

00:14:10.520 --> 00:14:16.080
At that moment she was standing
and just calling us Ivan Ivan.

00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:22.400
Come with me, sir, to the
hill, we saw the Lady.

00:14:22.480 --> 00:14:26.960
I didn't know what she
was really talking about.

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:28.880
I was a child of 16.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:31.600
I had never heard of a Lady.

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:36.120
However, at one point,
she threw her flip-flops.

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:38.080
She was on her feet.

00:14:38.160 --> 00:14:44.480
And she started running towards the
two of us and came closer to us.

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:47.360
She was now shaking with fear.

00:14:47.440 --> 00:14:50.320
The excitement was at its peak.

00:14:50.440 --> 00:14:55.320
In her trembling voice, she
called out, come with me.

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:59.160
Come with me, you'll see, it's the Lady.

00:14:59.240 --> 00:15:00.520
It's the Lady.

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:02.480
I knew Vicka before.

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:08.855
She was always a special temperament at
school and we always called

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:10.840
her Bojali at school.

00:15:10.920 --> 00:15:15.200
We were all afraid and
called her the sheriff.

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:17.880
True, she was a bit like that.
How she was.

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:19.200
She was fiercer.

00:15:19.280 --> 00:15:23.480
Little by little, I was
getting more and more afraid.

00:15:23.560 --> 00:15:26.640
When I went to school across the field.

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:31.720
Everyone wanted her to slow down
or speed up when they saw her.

00:15:31.800 --> 00:15:35.600
That's how it was, and
she and I said let it go.

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:42.040
What kind of Lady do I say to my friend,
Come on, we're late for the second half?

00:15:42.160 --> 00:15:45.800
However, she wasn't that
persistent, she says.

00:15:45.880 --> 00:15:48.480
Come on, go in peace, you'll see.

00:15:48.560 --> 00:15:52.840
We can see that something
strange is happening to her.

00:15:52.920 --> 00:15:59.160
It's not Vicka that I who we who I know
and who my friend knows so much better.

00:15:59.240 --> 00:16:02.160
She's even closer, lived next to him.

00:16:02.240 --> 00:16:08.480
At one point we decide, Come on, let's go
I on the right side on the left side,

00:16:08.560 --> 00:16:14.215
walking slowly with her, already knowing
what kind of temperament she's

00:16:14.240 --> 00:16:16.320
been through all that way.

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:18.760
You'll see when you get there.

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:21.760
It wasn't easy for us anymore either.

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:26.360
Just watching her behave and
our fear began to take hold.

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:32.840
We get to that place, it's a little closer
and we already see Ivanka and Mirjana.

00:16:32.920 --> 00:16:36.960
facing the hill crying and
just cuddling like this.

00:16:37.640 --> 00:16:44.880
And we come closer to them and Vicka turns
towards the hill and points with her hand.

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:45.640
Look up.

00:16:45.720 --> 00:16:52.055
I looked three times and I saw the
beautiful figure of Our Lady in normal

00:16:52.080 --> 00:16:58.720
size, illuminated by the light of the
star through us that was so expressive.

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:05.055
It wasn't that close, but you could really
see the outline of everything

00:17:05.080 --> 00:17:07.760
and it was floating on a cloud.

00:17:07.840 --> 00:17:11.640
My look didn't last
more than 10 15 seconds.

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:15.520
As soon as I saw it, I
immediately ran home.

00:17:15.600 --> 00:17:18.960
I mean, no one could have gotten there.

00:17:19.040 --> 00:17:24.040
When I got home, I didn't know
where my friend had stayed.

00:17:24.120 --> 00:17:29.040
I know he stayed, but I didn't
know what happened to him.

00:17:29.120 --> 00:17:32.200
I just wanted to be afraid of Zabok.

00:17:32.560 --> 00:17:33.920
The shock was a huge shock.

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:40.480
When I got home, I didn't tell anyone,
not even my parents or my brothers.

00:17:40.560 --> 00:17:42.960
I locked myself in my room.

00:17:43.040 --> 00:17:45.520
I can't describe that night.

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:52.440
The fear of what would happen, and the
questions that arose in me that night.

00:17:52.520 --> 00:17:55.000
As a sixteen-year-old child.

00:17:55.080 --> 00:17:56.560
Is that possible?

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.520
How is that possible?

00:17:58.600 --> 00:18:00.640
Was it really Our Lady?

00:18:00.760 --> 00:18:06.680
Until I was sixteen, I could never
even dream that it could happen.

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:11.440
I never had any special
devotion to Our Lady herself.

00:18:11.560 --> 00:18:16.680
I was a practical believer, I
went to religious education.

00:18:16.760 --> 00:18:22.855
Even the priests at that time didn't talk
much about the apparitions

00:18:22.880 --> 00:18:24.800
in Lourdes and Fatima.

00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:30.480
They had a classic religious education
that was built on other,

00:18:30.560 --> 00:18:32.520
more important things.

00:18:32.600 --> 00:18:38.800
So, I would say, it was no better
or worse than others in those years.

00:18:38.880 --> 00:18:43.600
But that night that was the
one that was ahead of me.

00:18:43.680 --> 00:18:50.400
It was a night of fear, a night of
anticipation of what was going to happen.

00:18:51.240 --> 00:18:53.580
Were you able to sleep at all?
I remember that.

00:18:53.800 --> 00:18:56.600
You once told me that you
were actually so afraid?

00:18:56.640 --> 00:19:01.015
You were in some kind of mixture of fear,
emotions, love, everything so quiet

00:19:01.040 --> 00:19:02.960
that even the window would darken.

00:19:03.040 --> 00:19:04.960
Everyone would come into the room.

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:06.560
What am I going to do, then?

00:19:06.880 --> 00:19:09.760
That's exactly what I wanted to say.

00:19:09.840 --> 00:19:13.200
I'm saying what I was most afraid of was.

00:19:13.320 --> 00:19:17.320
What if the Virgin Mary
comes to my room tonight?

00:19:17.440 --> 00:19:24.160
I'll try to escape where she'll escape to
because at that time I was 16 years old.

00:19:24.280 --> 00:19:29.415
I was so knowledgeable and shy that I
never walked in the dark

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:31.760
without my dad taking me to.

00:19:31.840 --> 00:19:38.360
In the village, when I watch a game or
basketball or he takes me and brings me.

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:42.400
When the game is over,
so I was scared and dark.

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:46.840
Just waiting for morning to
come as soon as possible.

00:19:46.920 --> 00:19:50.040
Morning is already coming to them all.

00:19:50.120 --> 00:19:53.520
I raise the blinds and I can already see.

00:19:53.600 --> 00:19:57.120
Mothers from the village
come to my mother.

00:19:57.240 --> 00:20:03.080
I see they're talking downstairs on
the lower plateau under the stairs.

00:20:03.160 --> 00:20:05.560
Did Ivan say anything to you?

00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:09.680
We heard that he was also
filming with the girls?

00:20:09.760 --> 00:20:11.320
Mother, he says no.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:16.520
And he immediately slowly walks
up the stairs towards my room.

00:20:16.560 --> 00:20:20.280
I can already see the
trembling in his voice.

00:20:20.360 --> 00:20:23.160
At that time fear begins to speak.

00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:28.600
Well, we heard something, open
the door, we need to ask that one.

00:20:28.680 --> 00:20:32.320
And I opened the door
to my mother and said.

00:20:32.800 --> 00:20:39.240
I saw it, but I'm still not sure
because it was 50, ten, fifteen seconds.

00:20:39.320 --> 00:20:45.800
You see everything, but you simply
can't be sure because you're not sure.

00:20:45.880 --> 00:20:47.400
And there we are.

00:20:47.480 --> 00:20:48.920
We stayed there.

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:52.120
I went down to the lower threshold.

00:20:52.200 --> 00:20:56.840
Then to the other mothers
who came from the village.

00:20:56.920 --> 00:21:04.200
I told the little one even more how it all
happened, as we have just talked about,

00:21:04.320 --> 00:21:10.520
and on that second day, a lot of
people and it started from all sides.

00:21:10.600 --> 00:21:12.200
It spread quickly.

00:21:12.320 --> 00:21:14.600
Podbrdo Međugorje, Čitluk.

00:21:14.720 --> 00:21:19.400
The authorities got on their
feet so that there were.

00:21:19.520 --> 00:21:23.680
A lot of Secret Services
monitoring everything.

00:21:23.760 --> 00:21:28.480
And we spent that whole day
together with the people.

00:21:28.560 --> 00:21:33.480
We watched with them, there
were others, we had no one.

00:21:33.680 --> 00:21:35.280
25.
June 25.

00:21:35.400 --> 00:21:39.080
June, so sometime in the afternoon.

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:46.400
An ambulance from Čitluk comes and
takes us to the student's clinic.

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:52.520
They pick us up without our
parents and without anything.

00:21:52.640 --> 00:21:59.895
I remember well, we came to the clinic
hallway where they are now in

00:21:59.920 --> 00:22:02.760
Čitluk, there was a clinic.

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:05.200
And now we meet there.

00:22:05.320 --> 00:22:07.120
And so the first.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:15.120
When Dr. Vujević was in Čitluk and we
entered his office, he was the first,

00:22:15.240 --> 00:22:19.280
while I did what I had to do with him.

00:22:19.360 --> 00:22:22.240
I had already gone outside.

00:22:22.320 --> 00:22:31.200
They had already come to pick them up and
take home all the drugs they had acquired.

00:22:31.320 --> 00:22:32.600
I was alone.

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:38.400
I stayed in the bank and I
don't know how to get home.

00:22:38.520 --> 00:22:44.000
My mother didn't come, and
no one came to my father.

00:22:44.120 --> 00:22:51.400
Only their parents came quickly and
picked me up and brought me home.

00:22:51.520 --> 00:22:58.655
And since my son was working for my
mother, sister, uncle, he drove

00:22:58.680 --> 00:23:01.960
the ambulance in Čitluk and he.

00:23:02.080 --> 00:23:06.400
He came out to meet me and returned home.

00:23:06.520 --> 00:23:14.760
By the time I got home, the others and
everyone else were already on the hill.

00:23:14.880 --> 00:23:18.560
And I had that meeting at my house.

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:20.800
with parents.

00:23:20.920 --> 00:23:23.160
That was the second day.

00:23:23.240 --> 00:23:26.440
That was the second day, and then.

00:23:26.520 --> 00:23:28.480
Then that second day.

00:23:28.560 --> 00:23:29.600
I was sure.

00:23:29.680 --> 00:23:33.920
She introduced herself
as the Queen of Peace.

00:23:34.000 --> 00:23:41.655
And while I was in the house, when I came
from the clinic, and to them, when they

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:48.175
were up on the hill, so that first day was
actually the second day of

00:23:48.200 --> 00:23:50.840
the encounter with Our Lady.

00:23:50.920 --> 00:23:52.040
That was it.

00:23:52.120 --> 00:23:54.760
It's hard to say it all now.

00:23:54.840 --> 00:23:59.880
It's hard to remember all
those moments, but for sure.

00:24:00.000 --> 00:24:07.615
I have a lot of things written down from
the first days of the apparitions that I

00:24:07.640 --> 00:24:11.400
can certainly talk about and a lot more.

00:24:11.480 --> 00:24:17.055
When the first day means introducing
myself as the Queen of

00:24:17.080 --> 00:24:19.640
Peace, the Queen, and that.

00:24:20.840 --> 00:24:21.400
Essentially.

00:24:21.480 --> 00:24:24.320
SE then forms this group of
six into six visionaries.

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:28.080
By the first day there were more
children, but they didn't go later.

00:24:28.240 --> 00:24:31.600
This friend of mine who
was with me the other day.

00:24:31.680 --> 00:24:37.215
He didn't, because when his sisters were
my five sisters, when they were as many

00:24:37.240 --> 00:24:39.720
as there were police in the village.

00:24:39.800 --> 00:24:43.800
They locked him in a room,
they didn't give him any ideas.

00:24:43.840 --> 00:24:45.360
Milka Marija's sister.

00:24:45.440 --> 00:24:47.280
Also, she didn't go either.

00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:49.440
She was afraid and the reason.

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:51.160
That's as far as I know.

00:24:51.240 --> 00:24:55.935
So the other day Jakov and Marija, Jakov
and Marija had that meeting

00:24:55.960 --> 00:24:57.880
together for the first time.

00:24:58.040 --> 00:24:59.800
Jakov was ten years old.

00:24:59.880 --> 00:25:01.560
Ten, fifteen, sixteen.

00:25:03.240 --> 00:25:05.800
Jakov was the youngest at ten years old.

00:25:05.840 --> 00:25:09.520
We were all sixteen, except
for Vicka who was seventeen.

00:25:11.160 --> 00:25:14.240
It is very interesting that there
was no parish priest at that time.

00:25:14.280 --> 00:25:15.960
The parish priest was Fr.
Jozo Zovko.

00:25:16.040 --> 00:25:16.800
He was on a trip.

00:25:17.400 --> 00:25:19.160
Jozo is Fra Jozo Zovko.

00:25:19.240 --> 00:25:21.360
I mean, I didn't know him.

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:23.320
I always say that well.

00:25:23.400 --> 00:25:24.800
I was there then.

00:25:24.880 --> 00:25:27.800
I was always at a distance with him.

00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:33.080
Not really much, I was an altar
boy, but I was always withdrawn.

00:25:33.160 --> 00:25:39.735
Our communication or that of the priest
was limited, very, very little, and then

00:25:39.760 --> 00:25:43.560
Fra Jozo was in Zagreb
for spiritual exercises.

00:25:43.640 --> 00:25:50.320
And by the time I arrived after three or
four days, he had returned to Medjugorje.

00:25:50.400 --> 00:25:52.000
And I remember well.

00:25:52.120 --> 00:25:56.640
When people were still from
the village to say chaplain.

00:25:56.720 --> 00:26:00.560
The chaplain at the time
was Fra Zrinko Čuvalo.

00:26:00.640 --> 00:26:01.200
To say.

00:26:01.280 --> 00:26:07.720
Then Zrinko said, "Let it go, it's just
children playing." That was his answer.

00:26:07.800 --> 00:26:10.880
When Fra Jozo came back and called us.

00:26:10.960 --> 00:26:17.615
I remember well the old cistern, and the
old cistern was right when you go to the

00:26:17.640 --> 00:26:24.335
church, where the statue is, when you go
in the middle towards the church, you can

00:26:24.360 --> 00:26:29.160
park your car, then that statue
and the glass in the glass.

00:26:29.240 --> 00:26:34.615
The only thing was that the cistern was an
old cistern and we sat

00:26:34.640 --> 00:26:36.560
on the cistern with him.

00:26:37.880 --> 00:26:43.240
He asked us about everything, how it all
started, those first days, and all that.

00:26:43.320 --> 00:26:45.720
That was our first meeting with him.

00:26:46.280 --> 00:26:47.640
He didn't believe you himself.

00:26:47.680 --> 00:26:49.880
He says he did from the beginning.
It was hard.

00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:51.320
It was like listen.

00:26:51.400 --> 00:26:54.280
It was a dream, it was a shock for us.

00:26:54.360 --> 00:26:55.560
A surprise, i.
e.

00:26:55.640 --> 00:26:58.200
it was a surprise for our parents.

00:26:58.280 --> 00:27:02.160
And our parents were at the beginning.
That was it.

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:04.320
It simply wasn't.
It wasn't.

00:27:04.400 --> 00:27:08.560
It wasn't simple, it wouldn't
seem that way even today.

00:27:08.640 --> 00:27:13.455
We were encountering something like this
for the first time, we

00:27:13.480 --> 00:27:15.240
had never had any idea.

00:27:15.280 --> 00:27:18.320
I've never read the book of apparitions.

00:27:18.400 --> 00:27:21.560
I've never had any idea about all of that.

00:27:21.640 --> 00:27:26.040
That's why I say, it was truly
a big, big surprise for me.

00:27:26.240 --> 00:27:28.920
What did you talk about then,
how did you communicate, pray?

00:27:28.960 --> 00:27:31.400
What was it like with the
gentleman in the beginning?

00:27:31.440 --> 00:27:33.040
How did you establish that contact?

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:35.720
Well, I think that was it.

00:27:35.800 --> 00:27:38.400
Some of us talked to her more.

00:27:38.480 --> 00:27:40.520
Some of us thought less.

00:27:40.600 --> 00:27:42.920
Vicka was her, I would say.

00:27:45.040 --> 00:27:46.375
The ringleader is the leader.

00:27:46.400 --> 00:27:51.280
That Vicka was, as they say,
professional, says Speak.

00:27:51.360 --> 00:27:54.680
This.
The spokesperson speaks to us.

00:27:54.760 --> 00:27:59.720
She led that communication
more openly than all of us.

00:27:59.800 --> 00:28:06.240
We were just listening to her more,
but later over time and over time.

00:28:06.320 --> 00:28:11.920
We opened up more and more to
the debate, but they were more.

00:28:12.000 --> 00:28:19.415
While the Gospa simply brought us back
through that time, encouraged us to relax

00:28:19.440 --> 00:28:23.200
a little because we were in a convulsion.

00:28:23.280 --> 00:28:30.695
Once each of our every meeting, entering
that meeting was simply an anticipation

00:28:30.720 --> 00:28:33.200
of what would happen today.

00:28:33.320 --> 00:28:35.520
What would happen today?

00:28:35.600 --> 00:28:42.895
But what was most profound for me in all
of that was the motherly love that she

00:28:42.920 --> 00:28:50.440
introduced us to, especially in the first
days, introduced us to all that we have.

00:28:50.560 --> 00:28:53.480
It wasn't overnight, but it was.

00:28:53.560 --> 00:28:55.880
But it's don't be afraid.

00:28:55.960 --> 00:28:57.160
I'm with you.

00:28:57.240 --> 00:28:59.160
She lays hands on us.

00:28:59.280 --> 00:29:02.400
Don't be afraid, I will guide you.

00:29:02.480 --> 00:29:06.600
I will give you messages
and everything else.

00:29:06.680 --> 00:29:12.680
I think that was the key thing to
strengthen us, to stabilize us.

00:29:13.040 --> 00:29:14.720
We were kids at that time.

00:29:14.760 --> 00:29:17.200
It wasn't that, it wasn't just that.

00:29:17.480 --> 00:29:20.440
Actually, there were a lot of
people coming in those days.

00:29:20.480 --> 00:29:23.695
Apart from this police, that policeman is
one of thousands of

00:29:23.720 --> 00:29:25.080
people who surrounded you.

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:28.280
They wanted you to actually ask
on their behalf, Mr. Protect.

00:29:28.360 --> 00:29:29.600
I don't think there was.

00:29:29.680 --> 00:29:36.455
There were many questions and questions,
for example, one of the many questions was

00:29:36.480 --> 00:29:42.600
Ask Our Lady how long will you be coming
like a day and I remember it well.

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:45.640
And Vicka asked that question again.

00:29:45.720 --> 00:29:51.135
When Our Lady stopped naked and got bored,
she and we never asked

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.800
that question again.

00:29:52.880 --> 00:29:58.335
But there was great pressure from the side
and especially when the

00:29:58.360 --> 00:30:00.000
hill was closing in.

00:30:00.080 --> 00:30:03.920
So we walked, looking
for a place in the field.

00:30:04.000 --> 00:30:10.855
One of the many places near here where we
as people met together to pray, and so we

00:30:10.880 --> 00:30:17.655
went to the sacristy in the church, then
from the church to another room where the

00:30:17.680 --> 00:30:22.735
priests were, then to the bell tower, and
all of those places

00:30:22.760 --> 00:30:24.720
were special even today.

00:30:24.800 --> 00:30:28.160
Today I stand here and I always remember.

00:30:28.240 --> 00:30:34.855
It always comes to me to those places and
everything that Our Lady said at those

00:30:34.880 --> 00:30:41.440
meetings and what she conveyed to us that
we convey the world and the hereafter.

00:30:41.520 --> 00:30:46.680
But the important thing for me
is always the important message.

00:30:46.760 --> 00:30:53.215
The message that Our Lady calls us to and
the time in which she comes to us, I

00:30:53.240 --> 00:30:59.855
didn't understand enough at first, what
Our Lady wants with her coming, but year

00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:06.255
after year throughout all these years I
realize that the simple message is to

00:31:06.280 --> 00:31:11.175
return to Jesus and return to Jesus,
because Our Lady never

00:31:11.200 --> 00:31:12.920
speaks about herself.

00:31:14.920 --> 00:31:21.175
She always directs us towards Jesus,
towards that source, and she directs

00:31:21.200 --> 00:31:24.200
us towards the words of the Gospel.

00:31:24.280 --> 00:31:31.655
But she wants to simplify that Gospel word
through her messages so that we understand

00:31:31.680 --> 00:31:38.720
it better, so that we can live better, and
so that it becomes a part of our lives.

00:31:39.000 --> 00:31:42.360
What are the main messages if you
could summarize them in a few words?

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:46.960
Well, we often times,
and often times people.

00:31:47.040 --> 00:31:54.295
I always say, these are the White Stones,
These are the five most important messages

00:31:54.320 --> 00:32:01.135
through which Our Lady leads us through
these years, and the central message is

00:32:01.160 --> 00:32:06.720
peace, peace in the heart, peace
in families, peace in the world.

00:32:06.840 --> 00:32:14.080
Because if there is no peace in a person's
heart, if there is no peace in the family,

00:32:14.160 --> 00:32:18.360
there can be no peace in
the world or in society.

00:32:18.440 --> 00:32:24.575
Peace always comes from the heart of a
person, and today the heart of a

00:32:24.600 --> 00:32:27.520
person is chained by sin and evil.

00:32:27.600 --> 00:32:31.800
Therefore, it is not when
it is not able to open.

00:32:31.880 --> 00:32:37.800
With that true true peace that
Christ, Our Lady says, leads to peace.

00:32:37.880 --> 00:32:39.680
And we only to Jesus.

00:32:39.760 --> 00:32:41.480
Peace can be absent.

00:32:41.560 --> 00:32:46.080
That is truly true peace,
that is life, that is love.

00:32:46.160 --> 00:32:51.040
And today, often when we speak
and think about ourselves.

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:53.280
The world can give peace.

00:32:53.360 --> 00:32:59.800
In that, we quickly become disappointed
because we see that it is fleeting.

00:32:59.880 --> 00:33:02.760
Only the Christian Jesus is peace.

00:33:02.880 --> 00:33:05.520
Jesus is joy, the love of life.

00:33:05.600 --> 00:33:12.440
The second message is also important, and
that is conversion to begin to change.

00:33:12.520 --> 00:33:19.640
To see ourselves, and to see ourselves, is
best through prayer, through confession,

00:33:19.720 --> 00:33:26.895
forsaking sins, and opening ourselves to
God through all of that and seeing, seeing

00:33:26.920 --> 00:33:32.455
the mirror of ourselves from within so
that we can receive grace

00:33:32.480 --> 00:33:34.160
and the Holy Spirit.

00:33:34.280 --> 00:33:41.455
It is always necessary to be clean in
order to heal the spirit in order to heal

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:46.120
physically and spiritually,
it is always necessary.

00:33:46.200 --> 00:33:51.960
Confession always needs to be
forgiven, it is always necessary.

00:33:52.040 --> 00:33:58.455
That is why Our Lady always repeats so
many times about forgiveness in

00:33:58.480 --> 00:34:01.760
confession, monthly confession, but.

00:34:01.840 --> 00:34:07.575
The second thing that she also wants to
emphasize in a special

00:34:07.600 --> 00:34:09.760
way that a person would.

00:34:09.880 --> 00:34:15.320
I would say, The most important
call is prayer of the heart.

00:34:15.400 --> 00:34:17.400
Prayer with the heart.

00:34:17.520 --> 00:34:23.040
I would say it nourishes our
peace and our hope and our love.

00:34:23.120 --> 00:34:25.120
And it strengthens us.

00:34:25.240 --> 00:34:30.960
Without peace, a person's body
dies, a person as a spirit dies.

00:34:31.040 --> 00:34:37.520
That is why prayer is, and I would
say the heart and soul of our faith.

00:34:37.600 --> 00:34:44.415
We must always pray, and that is a
process, a program for our life that we

00:34:44.440 --> 00:34:51.415
must decide on every day, decide to be
persistent and be patient and grow in

00:34:51.440 --> 00:34:57.335
holiness in good as well, and one call
that is also to which Our

00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:59.720
Lady calls us, is penance.

00:34:59.800 --> 00:35:03.160
Our Lady says in one of her messages.

00:35:03.240 --> 00:35:09.160
Through prayer, fasting, you can
stop natural disasters and wars.

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:15.000
When Our Lady says that, I wouldn't
say that, I don't say that.

00:35:15.320 --> 00:35:19.600
Our Lady says If Our Lady
says that, it is possible.

00:35:19.680 --> 00:35:22.600
Many think that work comes by mail.

00:35:22.680 --> 00:35:29.615
I would say that we cleanse ourselves, we
strengthen our spirit, we strengthen our

00:35:29.640 --> 00:35:33.280
faith and we owe the
security of our peace.

00:35:33.360 --> 00:35:40.535
Our Lady did not set an ultimatum when she
spoke about fasting that cannot become, it

00:35:40.560 --> 00:35:46.815
can replace work, prayer, some other
sacrifice, some other renunciation of

00:35:46.840 --> 00:35:51.800
something, giving up something
we love, that is dear to us.

00:35:51.880 --> 00:35:55.160
Except that a great gain is not a loss.

