00:52:22.400 --> 00:52:25.280
It is difficult to describe it in words.

00:52:25.360 --> 00:52:29.495
No matter how hard I have tried to
describe it all these

00:52:29.520 --> 00:52:31.400
years, it is inexplicable.

00:52:33.000 --> 00:52:34.400
Yes, that's interesting.

00:52:34.440 --> 00:52:38.480
Even if I'm not mistaken, it's a
joke that someone even made once.

00:52:38.720 --> 00:52:42.480
When that was, it was in the sacristy.

00:52:42.560 --> 00:52:47.640
On the right side, on the
right side of the altar.

00:52:47.760 --> 00:52:54.120
We had that apparition then and
that was that moment when they.

00:52:54.240 --> 00:53:00.695
They thought that there was a member of
the Commission on Zadar

00:53:00.720 --> 00:53:03.440
from Split that was before.

00:53:03.560 --> 00:53:12.055
And he was behind us during the press, he
was dressed in white, he was in white and

00:53:12.080 --> 00:53:17.440
during the apparition he
tried to do it with needles.

00:53:17.520 --> 00:53:20.600
I remember it very well.
Nothing.

00:53:20.680 --> 00:53:22.360
No.
Nothing has changed.

00:53:22.440 --> 00:53:23.240
It's Vicka.

00:53:23.320 --> 00:53:27.520
They just said Vicka, why do
you have blood on your back?

00:53:27.600 --> 00:53:30.280
On that white stripe, which she had.

00:53:31.440 --> 00:53:33.240
Another thing is how it is to have.

00:53:33.320 --> 00:53:36.960
You have a wife and children, you
sent recently, even a grandfather.

00:53:37.040 --> 00:53:41.240
So, the years go by and your life changes,
just like everyone else's and mine.

00:53:41.280 --> 00:53:43.160
People who look at us like they do.

00:53:43.200 --> 00:53:45.000
What is it like to live for them?

00:53:45.040 --> 00:53:46.320
I saw what life is like.

00:53:46.400 --> 00:53:50.880
Actually, here, maybe you could describe
to us a little bit how you live every day.

00:53:50.920 --> 00:53:54.800
You basically said that you wait for
an apparition from one to the next.

00:53:54.840 --> 00:53:58.535
However, what does life look like, the
daily life of a seer, and how

00:53:58.560 --> 00:53:59.960
do you live with each one?

00:54:00.360 --> 00:54:03.760
Since I live in America, I spend part of
the time there and part of the time here.

00:54:03.840 --> 00:54:04.840
Your wife is American.

00:54:06.480 --> 00:54:07.560
We met here.

00:54:07.680 --> 00:54:15.055
In 89, as a pilgrim, she came here with
two of her relatives, where after

00:54:15.080 --> 00:54:22.040
Medjugorje, and both of her relatives
were sent by Franciscan priests.

00:54:22.160 --> 00:54:25.960
and she became a rector in the church.

00:54:26.040 --> 00:54:29.840
So we met in 89 and got married in 84.

00:54:29.960 --> 00:54:35.560
We have four beautiful children,
two girls and two sons.

00:54:35.640 --> 00:54:42.840
The older daughter Christina got
married two years ago, three years ago.

00:54:42.960 --> 00:54:45.560
We now have a little baby.

00:54:45.640 --> 00:54:48.240
Not that there is one now.

00:54:48.360 --> 00:54:53.160
As we have already said,
Mikela is 25 years old.

00:54:53.240 --> 00:54:54.240
Daniel 25.

00:54:54.360 --> 00:54:56.360
Michaela 26.
And 25.

00:54:56.440 --> 00:55:00.960
And the youngest son
Mathieu is 18 years old.

00:55:01.040 --> 00:55:01.760
Listen.

00:55:01.840 --> 00:55:08.015
Many ask how I can implement everything
and how I can pass it

00:55:08.040 --> 00:55:10.120
all on to the family.

00:55:10.240 --> 00:55:14.040
Everything is this gift that God gave.

00:55:14.120 --> 00:55:17.440
We are one and we want to be one.

00:55:17.520 --> 00:55:19.440
We are one compact.

00:55:19.520 --> 00:55:24.440
We have great support as
the first great support.

00:55:24.520 --> 00:55:26.720
I have from my family.

00:55:26.840 --> 00:55:30.640
Everything I do outside in Medjugorje.

00:55:30.720 --> 00:55:38.015
When I am not at home with them, I have
great support and when I am with

00:55:38.040 --> 00:55:41.040
them, we are always in prayer.

00:55:41.120 --> 00:55:45.040
We are always together with each other.

00:55:45.120 --> 00:55:47.520
We support each other, we grow.

00:55:47.600 --> 00:55:53.720
There were challenging moments, especially
when the children started school.

00:55:53.800 --> 00:55:58.895
Knowing that at school they were all
Catholic, so at school you

00:55:58.920 --> 00:56:00.840
knew that I was the dad.

00:56:00.920 --> 00:56:04.120
Theirs is that I am in between, I speak.

00:56:04.200 --> 00:56:08.880
It was a little and a little
from the sides, but they are.

00:56:08.960 --> 00:56:14.775
I always told them, you have to be
witnesses, you have to have faith and

00:56:14.800 --> 00:56:18.000
you don't have to be afraid of anything.

00:56:18.080 --> 00:56:24.015
And the rest of them and their dignity and
their firmness remained on the

00:56:24.040 --> 00:56:26.280
mark and I am proud of that.

00:56:26.360 --> 00:56:27.720
And my wife, too.

00:56:27.800 --> 00:56:30.120
When she says, I am not here.

00:56:30.200 --> 00:56:34.800
She replaces all that and we
really live and try to live.

00:56:34.880 --> 00:56:40.320
We try to live Our Lady's messages
through every day through prayer.

00:56:40.400 --> 00:56:46.480
Through through meetings through when
we are at home in the family together.

00:56:46.560 --> 00:56:50.520
And that is a great gift
and a great gift for me.

00:56:50.760 --> 00:56:54.575
When I mentioned America, it is very
important to say that you don't have an

00:56:54.600 --> 00:56:57.840
apparition in America this afternoon
when you are in Medjugorje.

00:56:57.880 --> 00:56:58.360
The same.

00:56:58.400 --> 00:57:01.615
So, the apparitions are not related to
Medjugorje and the place

00:57:01.640 --> 00:57:02.840
itself, but they happen.

00:57:03.000 --> 00:57:06.880
They are apparitions there
from 8pm to 7am American time.

00:57:06.960 --> 00:57:10.160
And in Istanbul the
rosary also starts at 6am.

00:57:10.960 --> 00:57:13.200
When you mentioned time, I
used to hear some criticism.

00:57:13.240 --> 00:57:16.215
They say that the apparitions are, they
say, visionaries order Our Lady

00:57:16.240 --> 00:57:17.760
when she will come to them on order.

00:57:17.840 --> 00:57:20.040
It's good, it's an old tactic.

00:57:20.120 --> 00:57:23.800
Those who write and there are no orders.
You never did.

00:57:23.840 --> 00:57:24.280
Ordered.

00:57:24.320 --> 00:57:28.440
I don't have any orders from me
because I just listen to Our Lady.

00:57:28.480 --> 00:57:33.335
I just listen to Our Lady and that's what
they are the only ones with her all

00:57:33.360 --> 00:57:35.840
their lives for these 45 years together.

00:57:37.040 --> 00:57:38.520
Here Ivan, let's go slowly.

00:57:38.560 --> 00:57:40.600
Towards the end of the conversation.

00:57:40.640 --> 00:57:45.295
Somehow, could we use these 45 years as an
opportunity for the time to come, what

00:57:45.320 --> 00:57:50.055
would your message be from the position of
Medjugorje and the Medjugorje phenomenon

00:57:50.080 --> 00:57:54.455
and you personally, but also what it
conveys to the world, what message would

00:57:54.480 --> 00:57:58.055
the message of Medjugorje be for the world
and for people, for

00:57:58.080 --> 00:57:59.880
individuals, now just the globe.

00:58:00.200 --> 00:58:08.055
And I think this is so that the message
would be a message of gratitude for all

00:58:08.080 --> 00:58:11.960
that God has given us and is giving us.

00:58:12.080 --> 00:58:16.760
Throughout all these
years we must be grateful.

00:58:16.880 --> 00:58:24.920
We must be open, we must receive and begin
to live these gifts that God gives us.

00:58:25.040 --> 00:58:32.695
What I would especially like to emphasize
are two key things for me that are

00:58:32.720 --> 00:58:39.800
repeated non-stop, so to speak, so
often, and that is peace and prayer.

00:58:39.880 --> 00:58:45.680
All the other messages are
important, but peace is prayer.

00:58:45.760 --> 00:58:48.960
We must pray more, we must more.

00:58:49.040 --> 00:58:56.815
Today we live in a modern world, a world
of modern technologies, a world, new

00:58:56.840 --> 00:59:01.120
civilizations and the
challenges are great.

00:59:01.200 --> 00:59:02.520
Social Media.

00:59:02.600 --> 00:59:04.000
So much today.

00:59:04.120 --> 00:59:10.575
I would say that it affects the family and
young people, it puts

00:59:10.600 --> 00:59:12.680
pressure on families.

00:59:12.800 --> 00:59:14.080
And Our Lady.

00:59:14.160 --> 00:59:22.135
I often say what Our Lady says that today
Social Media is a new cancer that has

00:59:22.160 --> 00:59:26.120
metastasized today among young families.

00:59:26.240 --> 00:59:33.120
And a spiritual dimension today,
and families and society in general.

00:59:33.200 --> 00:59:34.400
And we must.

00:59:34.520 --> 00:59:42.775
I especially want to appeal to the family
that we need to return to tradition, not

00:59:42.800 --> 00:59:50.015
modernism, because tradition will take us
back to the old days where our

00:59:50.040 --> 00:59:54.440
grandparents taught us
about our true roots.

00:59:54.840 --> 01:00:01.175
Yes, yes, let us be a living tree and let
us water that tree with prayer, good

01:00:01.200 --> 01:00:04.480
things and here's what else I could say.

01:00:04.560 --> 01:00:07.720
We must live what Our Lady calls us to.

01:00:07.800 --> 01:00:14.415
This is not some wisdom of philosophy and
theology and we must live the messages

01:00:14.440 --> 01:00:20.175
that are in the call, and not go over them
and pass over them and wait

01:00:20.200 --> 01:00:22.680
for what will happen tomorrow.

01:00:22.720 --> 01:00:25.760
We must start living the same growth.

01:00:26.800 --> 01:00:31.800
People today are especially looking
for comfort and are ultimately afraid.

01:00:31.880 --> 01:00:36.375
It is a time of great wars and great
unrest in the world, how can

01:00:36.400 --> 01:00:38.320
it not be the end of it now?

01:00:38.400 --> 01:00:43.920
We talk to Our Lady about it, or rather,
what is Heaven's view of this situation?

01:00:44.000 --> 01:00:47.720
Should people live in fear
and how does it come about?

01:00:48.040 --> 01:00:51.600
Our Lady comes to us
as the Mother of Hope.

01:00:51.680 --> 01:00:57.215
She wants hope that she will bring us to
these days a tired world

01:00:57.240 --> 01:00:58.880
that has lost hope.

01:00:58.960 --> 01:01:06.015
But today we live in an environment in the
world where wars are so present and more

01:01:06.040 --> 01:01:11.200
pronounced that people suffer
so much, suffer where they are.

01:01:11.280 --> 01:01:13.240
Where is this BiH said.

01:01:13.320 --> 01:01:18.975
A struggle between good and evil between
God and Satan and we must

01:01:19.000 --> 01:01:21.000
stand on the right side.

01:01:21.120 --> 01:01:26.575
We must stand on the side that Our Lady
calls us to stand on the

01:01:26.600 --> 01:01:28.720
head of the dragon Satan.

01:01:28.800 --> 01:01:33.935
As Our Lady said in Fatima, she says I
want to finish what I

01:01:33.960 --> 01:01:35.880
started in Fatima here.

01:01:35.960 --> 01:01:42.975
Let us join, let us join that message and
yes, that we truly all together with her

01:01:43.000 --> 01:01:46.120
realize her plan that she comes with.

01:01:46.200 --> 01:01:47.720
That is important.

01:01:49.040 --> 01:01:50.520
Thank you, what can I say?

01:01:50.560 --> 01:01:55.535
Thank you for finding time for our viewers
and for me personally, of course, and for

01:01:55.560 --> 01:01:58.720
everything you've done over
the past forty-five years.

01:01:58.800 --> 01:02:02.040
Thank you for your perseverance
and unwavering courage.

01:02:02.080 --> 01:02:06.320
I know there are problems and setbacks,
but you hold on somehow, listen.

01:02:07.480 --> 01:02:10.040
I always say one thing.
I always say.

01:02:10.120 --> 01:02:15.600
I would like everyone to see Our Lady
because it would be much easier for me.

01:02:15.680 --> 01:02:18.080
I wouldn't be here with you today.

01:02:18.160 --> 01:02:21.880
But we must always remember
the words of the Gospel.

01:02:21.960 --> 01:02:25.440
Blessed are those who do
not see and yet believe.

01:02:26.640 --> 01:02:31.335
After all, that's what Our Lady herself
said when other people in those very first

01:02:31.360 --> 01:02:35.080
days that we've just returned to
said they too would like to see.

01:02:35.120 --> 01:02:38.775
Ask Our Lady, why don't we see Our Lady
and that's exactly what

01:02:38.800 --> 01:02:40.160
the Gospel message says.

01:02:40.200 --> 01:02:42.600
Here we end it with that.
Thank you again.

01:02:42.840 --> 01:02:43.320
AND.
To you.

01:02:43.400 --> 01:02:46.720
Dear viewers, thank you
and see you at some point.

